<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:22:09.360 --> 01:22:10.885
<font color="#808080">LINDA:</font> Oh, my God, Ronny!

01:22:11.240 --> 01:22:12.401
Ron!

01:22:12.640 --> 01:22:13.641
Open the bloody gate.

01:22:13.760 --> 01:22:14.727
<font color="#808080">WOMAN:</font> Will somebody
