- There's got to be something in here!

01:23:12.520 --> 01:23:14.249
Settle down!
<font color="#D900D9">(SHOUTING)</font>

01:23:14.320 --> 01:23:16.209
Zombies! Zombies!

01:23:16.320 --> 01:23:17.526
Ahh!

01:23:18.560 --> 01:23:21.325
If you get my hands on me, I'll kill you.

01:23:22.320 --> 01:23:23.970
<font color="#808080">NARRATOR:</font> <i>The world of the blind.</i>

01:23:24.040 --> 01:23:28.090
<i>Ron Burgundy, a man who had
flourished in a visual medium,</i>

01:23:28.160 --> 01:23:31.562
<i>had forever entered
this realm of darkness.</i>

01:23:31.840 --> 01:23:34.844
<font color="#D900D9">(SINGING)</font> <i>Always lonely</i>

01:23:35.360 --> 01:23:37.647
<i>Always looking</i>

01:23:39.120 --> 01:23:43.842
<i>To get even with the men
