01:36:30.400 --> 01:36:31.811
You must be Linda Jackson.

01:36:32.040 --> 01:36:33.451
You must be Veronica.

01:36:33.520 --> 01:36:35.010
Yes, I am. It's a pleasure.

01:36:35.200 --> 01:36:36.884
