picking up my mood.

01:36:58.080 --> 01:37:00.208
Well, I guess I'll leave you two alone.

01:37:00.280 --> 01:37:03.284
And it's been
an absolute pleasure, Ms. Corningstone.

01:37:03.480 --> 01:37:04.481
This has been great.

01:37:04.560 --> 01:37:06.369
