01:37:19.520 --> 01:37:22.285
in half an hour
at the Tishman School on 65th Street.

01:37:22.360 --> 01:37:24.886
And he wrote a piece for you, Ron.

01:37:25.080 --> 01:37:26.889
Aw, Walter.

01:37:26.960 --> 01:37:29.884
