01:40:05.880 --> 01:40:09.646
after turning my back on three of the
best friends anyone could ever ask for.

01:40:10.080 --> 01:40:11.286
Hi, Ron!

01:40:11.400 --> 01:40:13.084
So, if you'll excuse me,

01:40:13.160 --> 01:40:15.401
